{"tid":1451852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺「呢個係個伏」都係一個伏。","createTime":"2019-08-11T21:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T10:59:02.000Z","uid":51171,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"37cecdb9c85a3c0384f3958092b4c06af1064aa6","tid":1451852,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:14:40.000Z","msg":"喂，乜撚都係伏、係局，咁點分呀？<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手足，屌你咩，所以咪要每個人都要學識獨立思考同判斷囉！俾少少質素藍絲睇吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(唔肯定就唔好隨便推po &amp; 正負評。正負評有佢嘅參考價值，但你都要自己思考過，因為留低嘅正負評有可能係代表緊有一班冇腦嘅傻撚俾人呃左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。)"},{"pid":"d3f6904d6c25645df0a755955e5fcda0da43685a","tid":1451852,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:16:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bebaabcee9cc78ca4bb8b4cfe154647392ebc271","tid":1451852,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e3440a13183bc9b9ce21bb5a74da5587103651","tid":1451852,"uid":288830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:18:49.000Z","msg":"過嚟幫手獨立思考下！<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>裡邊係一啲優先唔會搞到市民嘅行動，圍機場、開放西隧大欖隧道，仲有好多好多方法！<br />\n<br />\n小妹同朋友有篇中長期戰術文有講，啱聽求幫推！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1444720/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1444720/page/1</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"df53855265fda50743ff602001b5b5b1192fdafd","tid":1451852,"uid":72590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:22:58.000Z","msg":"721 811<br />\n<br />\n獨立思考其實真係好重要<br />\n同埋對手要吹風一定會瘋狂正評自己嘅post，所以戰術戰略類我長期開部電影唔登入睇住正負皮再唔理內容都投少票嗰邊等人自己分析"},{"pid":"6c22ec3d70aa1cc77ad5cb321f1b7cd250151967","tid":1451852,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:36:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b061f65414cd872e2619a868660f7236730810e","tid":1451852,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:15:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"556f4ced3eaa64c995c0527a5b3b0af2dce74836","tid":1451852,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"298e8277a02e9103e28a6d4248054184ca890bfd","tid":1451852,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:59:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}